SCOPE — what this license does and does not cover

This MIT license applies ONLY to the original work in this repository: the
build script (build/), the web application (webapp/), the helper scripts, and
the documentation.

It does NOT cover the Line 6 FBV3 firmware. The stock firmware image
(Fbv3_v1_02_00.hxf) is the copyrighted property of Line 6 / Yamaha Guitar
Group and is not distributed here. The patched image this project produces is
a derivative of that firmware; you generate it locally from your own legally
obtained copy. Neither is licensed under the terms above. This project is an
unofficial, unaffiliated modification provided with no warranty.
